      • symbol

        public Symbol symbol​(LexicalUnit lexicalUnit)
        Create a new symbol based on the current state (text, line, column). The symbol is printed (using toString(LexicalUnit) to stdout. The symbols is added to symbols list. If the lexical unit is LexicalUnit.VARNAME, and the VarName is encountered for the first time, the value and the line of the symbol are added to identifiers
        Parameters:
        lexicalUnit - lexical unit associated to the symbol to create
        Returns:
        the created symbol object
